To get a deeper insights on asynchronous JavaScript, Promises, Async-await and even API data fetching, watch the video. You're also going to revisit the concept of object destructuring.

For this to work, you have to have node installed. So make sure to visit https://nodejs.org/en/, download and Install Node for your operating system, and you'll be good to go!

